==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foreslow
<hw>Fore*slow"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Forslow</er>.]</ety> <def>To make slow; to hinder; to obstruct.
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> See <er>Forslow</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No stream, no wood, no mountain could <qex>foreslow</qex>⟦br⟧
Their hasty pace.</q> <rj><qau>Fairfax.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foreslow</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Foreslow
<hw>Fore*slow"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To loiter. Same as
<er>Forslow</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forespeak</ent>⟦br⟧
